description: Sometimes you just get so angry that you need to flip a table over, throw a keyboard, or even throw some other people. It’s natural, we get it. If you have completely lost your mind to rage and need to let out a little steam, these emotes are here for you. Check out the last couple of emotes and see that you can go completely crazy and throw not one but two people! One in each hand! I don’t think you can express your anger any more clearly than this.
title: Flipping and Throwing Things
